        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Farm System Reform Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill places a moratorium on large concentrated animal feeding operations; requires country-of-origin labeling for beef, pork, and dairy products; and otherwise revises provisions related to the marketing of livestock, poultry, and meat.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
